---
import HawaiianIslands from "./HawaiianIslands.astro";
---
<section id="about" class="section scroll-mt-20">
  <div class="container-x">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
        <h2 class="h2-display" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
          How we got here, and where <span class="accent-script" style="color: var(--color-brand-red);">we’re going.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-6 max-w-md">
          <HawaiianIslands class="w-full h-auto" showLabel={true} />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-7 font-sans text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.6] flex flex-col gap-5"
           style="color: var(--color-ink-soft); max-width: 640px;">
        <p>
          The Foundation began as the <em>Hawai‘i Mobile Food Association (HiMFA)</em> — a
          working group of food-truck operators, organizers, and a small board pulling
          together articles of incorporation, bylaws, and a vendor master list across all
          the islands. As the work widened past trade-association scope, we re-chartered
          as the <strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">Hawai‘i Mobile Food Foundation
          (HiMFF)</strong> — a Hawai‘i 501(c)(3).
        </p>
        <p>
          Through <strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">Na Leo TV</strong>’s
          <strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">Community Creator Program</strong> —
          our local public-access channel on Hawai‘i Island — 15-minute cuts of our
          long-form podcast air on broadcast. Full 90-minute episodes live here on the
          Foundation site (and YouTube). Two episodes are in the can, more on the
          calendar.
        </p>
        <p>
          Mailing address: <strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">PO Box 59, Papaikou,
          HI 96781</strong>. Board recruitment is open. Articles, bylaws, and curriculum
          drafts are under cultural and legal review.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
